  The international supermodel shared a series of clips celebrating their romance with her 9.7 million followers on Wednesday. Heidi tied the knot with Tokio Hotel guitarist and songwriter Tom back in 2019. The pair are now celebrating their third anniversary, with Heidi documenting their love with a few more Instagram videos. Another clip saw them holding hands and running into the sea together, with Heidi writing: “Happy 3 Year Anniversary my LOVE. St.Barths August 3 2022.”  